            "body": "`-s <anyfile>` .. I've thought about this before.  Does the scriptfile need to be sourced again after restarting? I think it's unnecessary 🤔 because the --file is also discarded. updated commit msg for this if you want only skip `-s -` it can be \r\n```C\r\n  listitem_T *next = li->li_next;\r\n  if (next != NULL && strequal(tv_get_string(TV_LIST_ITEM_TV(next)), \"-\")) {\r\n    li = next;\r\n  }\r\n```",
