            "body": "That I'm not so sure about. I just copied that over from current `master` to not break existing functionality.\n\nEverything in v:argv should be fine as long as we don't expect UI changes from them.\nEg: In TUI :restart tests, we run `-c echo getpid()` on startup. But that just never shows up on screen after restart.",
