            "body": "> Everything in v:argv should be fine\r\n\r\n? I don't think it will work to \"restart\" with stdin files. \r\n\r\n```\r\necho foo | nvim --clean -s -\r\n:echo v:argv\r\n['nvim', '--embed', '--clean', '-s', '-']\r\n```",
